Trinity::

She looked around as her little spark started to calm down a bit.  
She took off in another direction.  She went down a small path that 
led to a large pond and a stream.  She smiled and went to the water's 
edge.  She looked at her reflection in the water.  She could see what 
she looked like, but used her imagination to see what she wanted to 
look like when she got older.  She stood there and smiled at her 
reflection and stared at the water.
